Stay in the heart of Barcelona – Excellent location - show map

One of our bestsellers in Barcelona! Located in the heart of Barcelona, Vincci Gala hotel offers luxurious rooms in a protected 19th-century palace. Free Wi-Fi is available.

The orginal façade, floor and central staircase of this unique hotel have all been preserved, creating a balance of traditional arquitecture and modern design.

The air-conditioned rooms include a private bathroom with hairdryer, free toiletries, and bath or shower. The rooms also come with a free laptop safe, extra large beds, satellite TV with pay-per-view channels, and a minibar.

A restaurant and snack bar are available on-site, and the hotel offers a breakfast buffet. Laundry and car rental services are available at a surcharge, and the property can provide tourist information.

Vincci Gala hotel is located opposite Urquinaona Metro Station, 2 minutes' walk from Plaça Catalunya Square. There are many bars, restaurants and shops in the surroundings, and you can reach Gaudi's La Sagrada Familia in 15 minutes by metro.

Eixample is a great choice for travellers interested in architecture, food and culture.

This is our guests' favourite part of Barcelona, according to independent reviews.

This property also has one of the best-rated locations in Barcelona! Guests are happier about it compared to other properties in the area.

Couples particularly like the location — they rated it 9.5 for a two-person trip.

This property is also rated for the best value in Barcelona! Guests are getting more for their money when compared to other properties in this city.

We speak your language!

Vincci Gala has been welcoming Booking.com guests since 17 Dec 2013.
 Hotel chain/brand: Vincci Hoteles

An inside look at Vincci Gala

Uniqueness and comfort are the terms that best define the Vincci Gala. The project includes the remodeling of a 1900s building, resulting in a unique hotel where tradition and design live together, thus respecting the city's Modernist essence.

Hotel surroundings – This neighbourhood is a great choice for travellers interested in architecture, food and culture – Check location Excellent location - show map Guests loved walking around the neighbourhood!

Children and extra beds

All children are welcome.

All children under 12 years are charged EUR 60 per night for extra beds.

All further older children or adults are charged EUR 60 per night for extra beds.

The maximum number of extra beds in a room is 1.

Any type of extra bed is upon request and needs to be confirmed by management.

Supplements are not calculated automatically in the total costs and will have to be paid for separately during your stay.
